  <brief_title>Safety and Biologic Activity Study of Gevokizumab to Treat Erosive Osteoarthritis of the Hand</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2 Proof-of-concept Study of Gevokizumab in Subjects With Inflammatory Erosive Osteoarthritis of the Hand</official_title>
